H0.text: What are the international registration letters of a vehicle from Iceland. IC

H1.text: What are the international registration letters of a vehicle from Iceland. ICE

H2.text: What are the international registration letters of a vehicle from Iceland. IL

H3.text: What are the international registration letters of a vehicle from Iceland. IS

A4.text: The United Nations uses ISO 3166-1 alpha-2 codes for international vehicle registration codes.

A5.text: The code IC is already reserved for the Canary Islands.
